{"tid":1837264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"因為一個夢困擾咗好耐","createTime":"2020-01-23T14:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T14:35:23.000Z","uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e496287f31e26c6be2395f6030b37f413af2dcdc","tid":1837264,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"個夢大概一年前開始發嘅<br />\n係個夢入面我係香港站搭緊條長電梯個個位<br />\n出入都係都要量體溫<br />\n我量體溫個陣就發現咗我有發燒<br />\n就即刻有個警察之類嘅人一槍打9我<br />\n之後有人同我急救<br />\n但我好快死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解而一年成日諗起或者係咁夢到<br />\n一年前會諗有咩可能警察會咁做<br />\n而七個月越來越覺得而個夢成真都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎 我老豆又話佢抵抗力好唔洗戴口罩<br />\n一係就戴made in China 嘅活性碳口罩<br />\n<br />\n嗚呀 我唔想死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e0887506fe646eb452d7ab53feedb264bb5eef","tid":1837264,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"潛意識太廢先會係夢到比人隊冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9af34a53a63d77ded673472042720a3ed584acc","tid":1837264,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e0887506fe646eb452d7ab53feedb264bb5eef","tid":1837264,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"潛意識太廢先會係夢到比人隊冧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:19:41.000Z","msg":"我係廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec005f8c7c767f9087640c3b6cc6af137bda6ce","tid":1837264,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9af34a53a63d77ded673472042720a3ed584acc","tid":1837264,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73e0887506fe646eb452d7ab53feedb264bb5eef","tid":1837264,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"潛意識太廢先會係夢到比人隊冧<img src=\"/asse